.TH "e1000_read_posted_mbx" 9 "e1000_read_posted_mbx" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
e1000_read_posted_mbx \- Wait for message notification and receive message
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "s32" e1000_read_posted_mbx
.BI "(struct e1000_hw *hw "  ","
.BI "u32 *msg "  ","
.BI "u16 size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hw" 12
pointer to the HW structure
.IP "msg" 12
The message buffer
.IP "size" 12
Length of buffer

returns SUCCESS if it successfully received a message notification and
copied it into the receive buffer.
